ncealed","start":43.62,"end":47.06},{"text":"The Lamb was still destined to be crucified on that fated hill","start":47.64,"end":56.5},{"text":"Yes the man on the middle cross bore the weight of man's","start":58.88,"end":68.48},{"text":"sins","start":68.48,"end":68.48},{"text":"He conquered the grave his love has no end","start":69.92,"end":80.48},{"text":"The one thief he mocked he knew not what he did But","start":82.6,"end":88.9},{"text":"the other thief believed","start":88.9,"end":91.7},{"text":"his eternity guaranteed","start":94.06,"end":101.44},{"text":"So which thief are you","start":103.96,"end":108.08},{"text":"A believer who is saved or a mocker who is lost","start":109.5,"end":114.48},{"text":"Who is he to you","start":116.06,"end":118.7},{"text":"You must decide Who is the man on the middle cross Admit","start":119.76,"end":128.34},{"text":"believe and confess Jesus as Lord","start":129.4,"end":136.5},{"text":"Admit","start":137.86,"end":139.26},{"text":"believe and confess Jesus as Lord Admit","start":140.48,"end":150.52},{"text":"believe and confess Jesus as Lord","start":152.28,"end":159.62},{"text":"Yes the man on the middle cross loves you so much more","start":160.7,"end":169.92},{"text":"than any love you've ever known","start":169.92,"end":175.04},{"text":"Just believe in his name and he will take you home Yes","start":176.04,"end":184.06},{"text":"the man on the middle cross bore the weight of man's sins","start":184.06,"end":193.52},{"text":"He conquered the grave his love has no end","start":193.52,"end":207.0}],"duration":207.0,"plain_text":"The scene unfolded, history being made The Son of God led to Calvary That very day, no guilt was found But the truth was concealed The Lamb was still destined to be crucified on that fated hill Yes, the man on the middle cross bore the weight of man's sins He conquered the grave, his love has no end The one thief he mocked, he knew not what he did But the other thief believed, his eternity guaranteed So which thief are you? A believer who is saved or a mocker who is lost? Who is he to you? You must decide Who is the man on the middle cross? Admit, believe and confess Jesus as Lord Admit, believe and confess Jesus as Lord Admit, believe and confess Jesus as Lord Yes, the man on the middle cross loves you so much more than any love you've ever known Just believe in his name and he will take you home Yes, the man on the middle cross bore the weight of man's sins He conquered the grave, his love has no end"}